Cell["\<\
Now find all repfigits in 25\[Hyphen]28 digit range. Takes maybe an hour \
(earlier versions took a couple of days at least).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.46351417082244*^9, 3.463514236663204*^9}}],

